🃏 Blackjack Game (Python Console Version)
This is a simple console-based Blackjack game implemented in Python. It mimics the classic card game where you play against the computer (dealer).

Features:
1.Draws cards from a deck (with simplified values).
2.Automatically handles Ace as 11 or 1 depending on your score.
3.Detects Blackjack and busts.
4.Lets the user choose to draw another card or stand.
5.Dealer draws until reaching at least 17.
6.Compares final scores and announces the result.
